Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.60,0:01:33.13,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,We saw a shooting star the other day...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.13,0:01:38.05,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...but Kagami said something about the\Nwishing three times thing being unrealistic.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.38,0:01:40.38,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Shooting stars are so wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.38,0:01:42.84,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I haven't seen many of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.84,0:01:45.35,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,It's difficult to see the stars from our house.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.76,0:01:46.56,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.56,0:01:48.56,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Since your house is in the city, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.81,0:01:50.52,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I would probably be too amazed...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.52,0:01:52.69,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...to have time to make a wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.27,0:01:55.61,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,The sight of a dazzling, shining star...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.61,0:01:58.03,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...would fill you with feelings of joy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.03,0:02:01.90,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,That could explain the myth \Nthat shooting stars grant wishes.
