Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.50,0:02:11.41,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,It's almost winter break.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.41,0:02:13.12,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,But we have finals first.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.33,0:02:16.46,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Do you have any plans for winter break?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.71,0:02:17.92,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.92,0:02:18.55,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Reminds me...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.55,0:02:20.84,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,We haven't taken a vacation in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.84,0:02:23.30,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I went to Asakusa the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.80,0:02:25.22,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,When was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.43,0:02:28.64,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,You know how you get sleepy \Non the train during winter?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.89,0:02:30.31,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She missed her stop?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.68,0:02:31.48,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.48,0:02:33.52,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,But isn't that the opposite direction?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.52,0:02:36.02,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,The train reached the end of \Nthe line and turned around...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.02,0:02:38.11,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...and then I missed my stop again...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.44,0:02:40.78,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,By the time I was conscious, we were in Asakusa.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.99,0:02:41.82,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Hey now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.82,0:02:44.86,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,You can only miss your stop so many times.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.12,0:02:48.87,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,But it wasn't entirely a bad thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.87,0:02:51.54,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Since I hadn't visited Asakusa in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.54,0:02:54.21,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't be doing that right before finals.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.87,0:03:00.76,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,And I had a feeling I saw a girl in a\Nsailor uniform with a machine gun walk by...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.76,0:03:02.67,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,What was that about?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.88,0:03:05.26,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me someone was making a hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.26,0:03:06.30,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,And you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.30,0:03:08.39,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Sleeping more helps you grow more!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.39,0:03:09.68,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're growing?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.97,0:03:11.39,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I got an even better one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.77,0:03:15.06,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,My dad pulled an all-nighter \Nand then went to turn in a manuscript.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.06,0:03:17.48,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,He got on an early-morning train but missed his stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.48,0:03:19.48,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...then it reached the end and made a U-turn...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.48,0:03:21.36,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...and when he woke up, he'd already missed his stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.36,0:03:23.19,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...and this happened a few more times.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.19,0:03:27.03,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,He started to wake up when \Nhe got close to his station...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.99,0:03:27.20,ls_alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}Patrasche...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.03,0:03:29.78,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...but he still ended up missing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.20,0:03:29.78,ls_alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}I'm so tired...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.91,0:03:34.37,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,He was tired and wanted to get\Nhome and sleep, but he couldn't get home.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.50,0:03:37.67,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,In the end, he no longer knew...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.67,0:03:42.88,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...which direction he was going whenever he woke up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.88,0:03:44.09,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Unbelievable...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.09,0:03:48.09,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I still wake up before my stop when I fall asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.09,0:03:49.30,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,That's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.30,0:03:50.72,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,How do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.72,0:03:53.06,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Maybe she has an internal alarm clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.06,0:03:55.52,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Though it doesn't work all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.52,0:03:56.23,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.56,0:03:58.35,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Since she's always snacking away.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.69,0:03:59.69,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.11,0:04:02.40,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,But train seats are really warm...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.40,0:04:04.24,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...so you get really sleepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.40,0:04:05.65,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.65,0:04:07.41,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,It's all warm and fuzzy...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.41,0:04:10.66,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...like you're sitting next to \Nthe window in the classroom...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.66,0:04:11.91,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...on a sunny winter afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.91,0:04:12.79,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.79,0:04:14.66,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Covering for each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.66,0:04:16.71,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I-It's not like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.96,0:04:17.67,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,The other day...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.67,0:04:19.29,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,When I tried to wake you up on the ride home...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.75,0:04:20.96,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Hey, wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.96,0:04:21.88,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,We're there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.88,0:04:24.51,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Just five more minutes...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.51,0:04:25.67,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I mean it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.84,0:04:27.43,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,She yelled out half-asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.43,0:04:29.34,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Everyone around us was laughing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.68,0:04:33.60,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,One of my friends did that in class once.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.60,0:04:34.52,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Sheesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.52,0:04:36.31,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Birds of a feather.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.85,0:04:37.94,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're grouping us together?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.44,0:04:40.31,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,But why five minutes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.31,0:04:43.57,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Well, if you went to wake someone up\Nand they were like, give me another hour...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.57,0:04:44.82,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...wouldn't you be pissed?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.82,0:04:46.19,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Well, that's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.19,0:04:50.36,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...but five minutes comes up \Nin a lot of other situations.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.36,0:04:51.95,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Like, just wait five minutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.58,0:04:53.16,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,You have a point.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.62,0:04:56.62,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Maybe 'cause it isn't too long or too short?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.62,0:04:59.75,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Though the five-minute wait \Nfor a train feels really long.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.75,0:05:00.96,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Sure does!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.17,0:05:02.54,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.54,0:05:03.79,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,But then again...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.13,0:05:05.88,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,People who say to wait five minutes...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.88,0:05:08.72,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...tend to make you wait a lot longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.97,0:05:13.72,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,You know how people say to not use\Nyour cell or put on makeup on the train?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.01,0:05:18.64,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,But it's a lot worse when the \Nperson next to you leans on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.23,0:05:20.52,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,They're so heavy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.52,0:05:23.90,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,And you end up wanting to \Nstand after managing to get a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.19,0:05:27.94,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,And when you're stuck with \Nthe sticky head of an old person...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.94,0:05:31.74,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Sometimes, I try to shove them off...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.74,0:05:36.33,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...but they somehow manage to\Nkeep returning to the same position.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.66,0:05:37.45,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.45,0:05:38.62,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,It's a mystery.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.91,0:05:40.75,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,When I fall asleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.75,0:05:44.21,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...and there's a man on one \Nside and an empty seat on the other...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.21,0:05:46.84,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...I try to lean myself towards the empty seat...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.84,0:05:50.13,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...but for some reason, I always \Nend up leaning the other way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.30,0:05:54.10,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Guess your body feels more \Ncomfortable leaning a certain way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.35,0:05:57.39,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,When I see someone leaning over...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.39,0:06:00.02,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...I shrink up like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.02,0:06:02.69,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...then their elbow hits my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.98,0:06:05.23,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Doesn't that mean they're actually awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.65,0:06:06.61,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.02,0:06:07.40,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.40,0:06:08.23,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Bye-bee!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.23,0:06:09.15,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.53,0:06:11.15,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,You know how...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.15,0:06:13.45,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...some people at our school \Ntake the inbound train home...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.45,0:06:16.08,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...and some people take the outbound train home?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.95,0:06:22.08,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Don't the ones who take the\Ninbound train look more refined somehow?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.08,0:06:23.79,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Since Yuki-chan's an inbounder.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.58,0:06:25.50,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,That's not...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.50,0:06:26.54,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.54,0:06:29.38,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Back to the farm, fellas.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.19,0:06:52.70,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.70,0:06:54.53,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is the stop before.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.70,0:07:01.00,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.16,0:07:05.08,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I didn't get any studying done yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.96,0:07:09.30,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I actually put in a lot of effort this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.30,0:07:10.96,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,If I do say so myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.28,0:07:13.42,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,How much studying did you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.84,0:07:15.22,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Only four hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.84,0:07:15.22,ls_alt,,0,0,0,,A whole four hours!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.30,0:07:16.97,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.10,0:07:21.18,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,You're good at everything, Kagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.18,0:07:24.27,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Well, I do a lot of studying.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.27,0:07:25.52,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Just between you and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.77,0:07:29.11,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,You're definitely really competitive.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.36,0:07:30.07,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.07,0:07:32.40,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's my pride as the older sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.40,0:07:36.78,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I feel like I have to be ahead of Tsukasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.78,0:07:39.62,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Though I usually say neither \Nof us is really older or younger.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.62,0:07:41.58,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I used to be pretty worried about that stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.95,0:07:45.75,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,But Tsukasa probably wasn't much competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.17,0:07:47.54,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Well, that's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.54,0:07:48.96,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Stupid Kona-chan thinks she's all that!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.34,0:07:51.50,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,It's almost Christmas!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.76,0:07:54.22,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I wonder what my present will be this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.22,0:07:56.26,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,You still get presents...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.13,0:08:00.47,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,How long did you believe in Santa Claus?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.77,0:08:04.73,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Santa Claus isn't real?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.73,0:08:05.56,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Holy cow!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.98,0:08:08.94,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Santa never came to Konata's house...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.94,0:08:12.07,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...so her dad gave her presents in his stead.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.07,0:08:15.03,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,That's why she thought he might be out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.03,0:08:16.03,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,That old man...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.03,0:08:18.57,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,He really wants to look good \Nin front of his daughter, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.95,0:08:20.49,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Hey, Hiiragi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.49,0:08:22.33,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Hiiragi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.33,0:08:23.66,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Here's the handout from before.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.20,0:08:24.79,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Gotcha.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.08,0:08:26.79,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,And then, Hiiragi-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.12,0:08:28.87,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Hiiragi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.87,0:08:30.17,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,You dropped your pencil.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.58,0:08:31.29,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.63,0:08:33.21,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Hey, Kagami!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.92,0:08:34.80,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Kagami-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.80,0:08:36.30,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Here's the handout from earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.97,0:08:37.38,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.68,0:08:39.89,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Sebastian, like. stinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.47,0:08:41.22,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Kagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.22,0:08:42.47,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,You dropped your handkerchief.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.81,0:08:43.47,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Holy cow?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.89,0:08:47.85,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Maybe I go to Tsukasa's class a little too much.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.52,0:08:51.23,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,My cavity started hurting recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.23,0:08:52.69,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,My, how dreadful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.07,0:08:55.19,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I really can't stand dentists.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.74,0:08:58.28,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,You went to see the dentist \Nfor your cavity the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.28,0:08:59.70,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Is it better now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.11,0:09:04.29,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Dentists take a long time on each tooth...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.29,0:09:06.79,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...and they have to repeat \Nthe procedure for every tooth...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.79,0:09:09.46,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...so it takes a long time, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.46,0:09:12.29,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,So I ended up escaping...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.29,0:09:13.67,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...after making a number of excuses.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.30,0:09:15.30,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,What to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.30,0:09:16.76,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She sounded all cutesy...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.76,0:09:18.63,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...but that's pretty crazy!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.97,0:09:19.93,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Konata!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.51,0:09:23.01,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Wanna go wild with everyone on Christmas?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.01,0:09:23.97,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.97,0:09:25.85,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I already have plans for Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.43,0:09:26.97,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.97,0:09:28.14,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Is it a man?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.81,0:09:29.69,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.06,0:09:32.90,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Are you going somewhere with your dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.90,0:09:33.48,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.48,0:09:36.23,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I told Dad that I'd be home late.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.65,0:09:37.49,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Don't tell.me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.49,0:09:39.61,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,You're really going on a date with your boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.61,0:09:40.49,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,When did you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.49,0:09:42.24,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Sorry to disappoint you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.24,0:09:43.74,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...but I'm just working.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.33,0:09:44.99,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.99,0:09:48.25,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Almost all the customers are male so I wasn't lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.42,0:09:50.04,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Thought you'd managed to get ahead of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.04,0:09:51.17,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,You got me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.42,0:09:54.04,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,There's a special event on Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.29,0:09:57.38,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,We dress like Santa CIaus for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.67,0:09:59.88,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,You really love that kind of stuff, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.52,0:10:01.38,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,But you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.72,0:10:04.93,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,You guys also cosplay as \Nshrine maidens for New Year's.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.93,0:10:06.39,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,At your temple.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.39,0:10:07.85,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Don't call it cosplay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.81,0:10:10.14,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.14,0:10:12.06,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,It's good that Santa Claus gives everyone presents...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.98,0:10:17.15,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...but ever since I was little, \NI was like, he's totally trespassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.15,0:10:20.19,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't look down on \Nsomething based on a holy man.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.19,0:10:21.86,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Spiteful brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.86,0:10:22.61,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Still...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.16,0:10:28.83,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Santa is supposed to give children dreams...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.83,0:10:32.46,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...so what's with the men who \Nturn to this squirt with their dreams?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.46,0:10:33.42,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.42,0:10:35.54,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,You just casually insulted a lot of people?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.04,0:10:39.09,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,And is it okay for you guys to celebrate Christmas?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.09,0:10:39.71,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.71,0:10:42.42,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,We usually got Christmas presents, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.42,0:10:45.43,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,We worship every god there is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.85,0:10:48.22,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,We regularly visit temples.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.81,0:10:51.23,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,And we sang in a church choir once.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.56,0:10:53.98,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Sounds peaceful.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.48,0:10:55.44,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.77,0:10:55.44,ls_alt,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.44,0:11:00.69,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,A shrine maiden said she wanted\Nto get married in a wedding dress...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.69,0:11:02.57,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Is that okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.57,0:11:04.95,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't that be a little complicated?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.49,0:11:09.33,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.33,0:11:11.00,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Getting chilly these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.37,0:11:13.04,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Cousin Yui, welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.04,0:11:14.29,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Whatcha watching?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.71,0:11:16.42,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,A detective show.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.96,0:11:17.96,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Any good?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.96,0:11:18.88,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.88,0:11:19.88,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Nothing else to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.63,0:11:21.92,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Okay, I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.92,0:11:23.42,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,That man's the killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.76,0:11:25.26,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Please wait, Officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.26,0:11:27.55,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,There's something odd about this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.55,0:11:28.97,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Nothing odd at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.97,0:11:30.39,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Case closed!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.39,0:11:31.10,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,What's with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.10,0:11:31.97,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,This has nothing to do with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.23,0:11:35.85,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,This is why cops are useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.85,0:11:37.98,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Aren't you a cop yourself...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.77,0:11:41.69,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Why'd someone have to call now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.69,0:11:44.32,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,They're about to reveal the killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.32,0:11:45.57,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,How can you tell?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.57,0:11:45.86,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.86,0:11:46.66,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.66,0:11:48.49,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,You're the killer, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.49,0:11:49.87,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,No use in hiding it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.24,0:11:54.46,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I wonder why these two-hour\Nshows always end on the edge of a cliff.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.46,0:11:59.63,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Maybe cause people aren't willing to\Nact until their back's against the wall?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.92,0:12:01.13,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Yahoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.13,0:12:02.25,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,How ya doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.25,0:12:03.80,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Cousin Yui, evenin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.80,0:12:05.51,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Whatcha watchin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.51,0:12:07.47,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,A movie for a popular detective show.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.47,0:12:09.14,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Dad rented it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.30,0:12:11.81,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Crimes don't happen in conference rooms!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.81,0:12:13.02,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,They happen at the scene!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.18,0:12:14.60,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,No, no, that's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.60,0:12:16.64,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Nobody ever gets that passionate.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.64,0:12:18.27,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yet you reject that...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.52,0:12:19.56,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Pretty sure that...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.56,0:12:24.07,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...the receipts were stolen at the behest of the chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.44,0:12:26.78,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,This is why he fails.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.78,0:12:28.57,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You know what's going on?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.95,0:12:29.57,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.57,0:12:31.53,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,They eat pork bowls a lot in police shows...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.53,0:12:33.41,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...but apparently, that isn't actually allowed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.41,0:12:34.83,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Well, it's fiction...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.83,0:12:36.21,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...so a lot of it's probably made-up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.87,0:12:40.46,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,So police commissioners' \Ngranddaughters aren't really like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.00,0:12:42.54,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Police commissioners' granddaughters?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.54,0:12:44.38,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Well, I've never met one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.38,0:12:46.51,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I'd at least want Mai-chan to exist...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.51,0:12:47.55,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,To give me hope...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.55,0:12:49.34,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Empty dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.22,0:12:53.93,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,There sure are a lot of cases \Nwith adults going after children.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.93,0:12:55.14,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Indeed...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.14,0:12:56.73,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I've been thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.98,0:12:59.60,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,If you teach kids martial arts...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.60,0:13:01.73,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...wouldn't there be a decrease in that stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.11,0:13:04.53,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,After intensive training...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.53,0:13:08.53,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...Master Oyama was able to beat a\Ncow with his bare hands, with one blow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.53,0:13:11.45,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,And bears toppled like trees after a couple of hits!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.45,0:13:12.62,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.99,0:13:16.37,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,But won't that come back to haunt you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.37,0:13:17.87,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,When those kids grow up...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.87,0:13:19.42,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...the adults will be strong, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.08,0:13:21.67,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.67,0:13:23.00,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.00,0:13:24.63,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,People say training in the martial arts...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.63,0:13:27.88,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...helps you mature as a person.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.88,0:13:28.88,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.26,0:13:29.63,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.13,0:13:33.97,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,There's someone who does martial\Narts and hasn't matured right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.43,0:13:35.64,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,How rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.89,0:13:36.85,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.85,0:13:41.65,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I have this cousin, Cousin Yui's little\N sister, who's entering high school next year.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.90,0:13:43.31,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,She's physically weak...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.94,0:13:44.57,ls_alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Cousin Konata!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.31,0:13:46.36,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...but she's sweet and pure and really adorable.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.48,0:13:53.16,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,But when I start thinking about how a\Nhealthy spirit leads to a healthy body...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.45,0:13:58.29,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,....I start feeling like something dark\Nis lurking behind those shining eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.29,0:14:00.91,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I doubt aphorisms are universal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.91,0:14:02.17,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Look at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.42,0:14:04.29,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,The year's almost over.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.29,0:14:07.92,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Once it's December, you always \Nfeel like the year flew by so fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.26,0:14:11.97,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Are you going to help out at your\Ntemple as shrine maidens again this year?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.97,0:14:13.01,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.01,0:14:14.93,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Come draw your fortune again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.18,0:14:16.26,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,With fortunes...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.26,0:14:20.06,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,If you get really bad luck, it's an unpleasant feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.18,0:14:21.39,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,But if you get really good luck...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.39,0:14:24.81,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...it feels like you already wasted \Nyour luck for the year, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.81,0:14:27.98,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Well, that's why people say average luck is best.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.32,0:14:29.23,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.23,0:14:31.61,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Then here's an early present from your teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.61,0:14:32.95,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Here are your report cards!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.91,0:14:35.53,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,How did you do, Kona-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.91,0:14:35.53,ls_alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Here! Good work!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.58,0:14:37.49,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.49,0:14:39.29,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I don't want this present!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.29,0:14:43.42,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,We give presents based on effort in my school of Santa.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.42,0:14:44.71,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Think on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.71,0:14:47.21,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Like a bonus to your winter homework.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.54,0:14:50.96,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I wonder what kind of Christmas \Ncakes will be good this year!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.96,0:14:52.38,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,When you go to a bakery...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.38,0:14:54.26,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...there are so many cute cakes...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.26,0:14:57.10,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...that you can have fun just looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.10,0:15:00.68,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,What happens to the cakes \Nthat weren't sold before Christmas?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.68,0:15:04.19,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Perhaps the employees take them home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.19,0:15:08.23,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,But if nobody takes them, \Nthey might throw them away.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.23,0:15:11.86,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,They often compare marriage to Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.24,0:15:13.82,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Like how twenty-five is the end of the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.24,0:15:17.99,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Once you're past twenty-five, \Na Christmas cake is just another cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.99,0:15:20.99,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,After one night, it's just another decorated cake...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.99,0:15:22.54,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...that suddenly looks stale...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.54,0:15:24.79,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...so you lose your appetite.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.25,0:15:28.59,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I was talking about Santa Claus \Nwith Kona-chan the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.59,0:15:30.88,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,How long did you believe in Santa, Yuki-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.26,0:15:34.88,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,It feels like you would have \Nbeen a true believer like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.88,0:15:37.59,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I also believed in Santa Claus.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.97,0:15:41.68,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,When I was little, I tried to send a\Nletter of gratitude to Santa Claus...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.68,0:15:44.10,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...and did some research.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.10,0:15:47.23,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,But I didn't learn much after asking my parents...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.23,0:15:49.11,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...so I did some thorough investigating...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.40,0:15:51.44,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...and learned of the people Santa Claus was based on...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.44,0:15:54.15,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...and once I saw the phrase \N"origin of Santa Claus" pop up...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.15,0:15:56.86,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...my dreams were quickly shattered.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.28,0:16:00.53,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,How'd you do, Miyuki-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.53,0:16:01.54,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Lemme see!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.37,0:16:04.04,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Just what you would expect from Yuki-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.04,0:16:05.41,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I could never do so well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.29,0:16:08.92,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I feel a little pissed about losing...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.92,0:16:12.55,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Yuki-chan's at the top of our class so it's hopeless...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.55,0:16:14.17,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,We could never beat her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.38,0:16:14.97,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.97,0:16:16.88,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I don't care about grades...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.88,0:16:17.84,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...but stuff like bust size...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.84,0:16:18.80,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Look! Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.30,0:16:21.60,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm hungry.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.60,0:16:23.56,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll have a cup of ramen.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.97,0:16:24.93,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Not done yet?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.93,0:16:28.77,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,{\i1}These three minutes of waiting feel really long.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.35,0:16:31.57,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll use this to kill time today.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.82,0:16:35.03,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,And then your noodles end up soggy, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.03,0:16:35.86,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.86,0:16:38.49,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,The extra broth for my cup fried soba dried up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.49,0:16:39.57,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,You people...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.66,0:16:45.62,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She told me she would be late...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.62,0:16:46.66,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But this is too late!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.16,0:16:48.58,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't let her make a habit of this.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.58,0:16:50.71,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Need to give her a stern \Ndressing down every now and then.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.71,0:16:52.29,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As the man of the house.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.29,0:16:53.88,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.88,0:16:54.59,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Konata!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.59,0:16:55.51,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Come here for a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.09,0:16:56.88,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,What time do you think it i—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.88,0:16:58.13,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Merry Christmas!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.43,0:17:01.72,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,This is my Christmas present for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.05,0:17:04.14,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,It must have been cold outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.14,0:17:05.35,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Want some hot tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.35,0:17:05.85,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.85,0:17:06.89,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I do! I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.89,0:17:09.44,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I'm so happy I could die.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.44,0:17:10.52,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.52,0:17:11.98,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,G'day!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.90,0:17:14.98,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Cousin Yui's here to save the day!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.98,0:17:16.32,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,You stink of alcohol!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.32,0:17:17.82,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,It's dangerous to DUI!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.49,0:17:21.32,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I parked the car somewhere and had a drink nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.32,0:17:22.49,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.49,0:17:25.37,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,It's Christmas Eve yet my husband's not here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.37,0:17:27.20,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Our plans tonight are...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.20,0:17:27.79,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Cousin Yui...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.79,0:17:30.21,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't you go to your parents'\Nplace instead every once in a while?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.54,0:17:33.09,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.09,0:17:33.75,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Yui?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.75,0:17:34.84,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.84,0:17:36.71,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I was going to sneak in and surprise you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.71,0:17:38.03,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...but it was locked.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.55,0:17:39.51,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Are you at your parents' place?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.80,0:17:40.38,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I'm coming home!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.68,0:17:42.47,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Right away at full speed!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.47,0:17:44.35,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Running every light on the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.35,0:17:47.39,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Seriously, you shouldn't be breaking the law.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.39,0:17:48.64,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I'll drive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.81,0:17:51.02,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I've got a little time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.02,0:17:52.85,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I'll log in for a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.19,0:17:53.52,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.52,0:17:54.85,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Teacher's on.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.49,0:18:00.15,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.15,0:18:01.41,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Let's go crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.41,0:18:03.57,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Until morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.29,0:18:07.70,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Please wait one moment.
