Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.97,0:18:25.01,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I was here last Sunday to buy manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.39,0:18:27.89,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Don't get why you pay the fare to come here so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.89,0:18:29.22,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Even if it's for the points...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.22,0:18:30.39,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...this is pretty excessive.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.39,0:18:31.52,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,You really love this stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.98,0:18:35.69,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Besides, do you even use the prizes they give?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.44,0:18:37.52,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.52,0:18:38.90,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Thought so.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.90,0:18:41.28,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,That kind of stuff is hard to use.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.49,0:18:42.45,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Yep. Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.45,0:18:44.53,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,lt'd be a waste to use.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.53,0:18:46.49,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Their value would go down.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.49,0:18:48.99,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh, so that's how it is...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.99,0:18:49.75,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Whatever.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.21,0:18:54.79,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.79,0:18:55.54,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.79,0:18:58.17,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Didn't you get shocked by static electricity?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.17,0:18:59.00,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.50,0:19:00.63,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Why's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.63,0:19:03.30,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Konata's always sitting in front of the computer...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.30,0:19:05.76,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...so her body's already full of weird waves?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.76,0:19:08.06,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Still, I really can't stand winter.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.06,0:19:11.39,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,And I heard you can get shocked \Njust by touching someone's hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.98,0:19:12.60,ls_alt,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.23,0:19:15.02,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Are you sure you two don't really hate each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.93,0:19:13.44,ls_alt,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.60,0:19:14.06,ls_alt,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.39,0:19:14.98,ls_alt,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.02,0:19:15.94,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Holy cow.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.06,0:19:15.94,ls_alt,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.28,0:19:22.11,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Whatcha doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.11,0:19:23.99,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Oh, I wanted to try it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.03,0:19:27.03,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.75,0:19:34.04,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Good lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.96,0:19:37.46,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I'm your navigator, Akira Kogami!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.46,0:19:40.46,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,We're already on the eleventh \Nepisode of Lucky Channel!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.46,0:19:42.13,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,And on this eleventh episode...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.13,0:19:47.43,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...I have some wonderful news \Nyou've all been waiting for!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.55,0:19:48.26,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,U-Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.60,0:19:50.43,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Everybody's sent in...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.60,0:19:52.47,ls_alt,,0,0,0,,She's really in it today.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.43,0:19:53.39,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...lots of passionate letters...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.39,0:19:57.19,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...asking for Akira to show up in the actual show!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.77,0:19:57.73,ls_alt,,0,0,0,,H-Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.19,0:19:59.40,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,On the next episode, I, Akira Kogami...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.73,0:19:59.40,ls_alt,,0,0,0,,I'm the assistant Minoru Shiraishi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.40,0:20:00.36,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Zip it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.36,0:20:03.11,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...will be showing up in the actual show!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.11,0:20:03.11,ls_alt,,0,0,0,,But I need to introduce myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.36,0:20:07.57,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Thank you to Konata Izumi from\NSaitama along with everyone else...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.57,0:20:09.24,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...who sent postcards to Newtype!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.08,0:20:11.33,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,So Akira-sama's also making an appearance?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.37,0:20:15.83,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,What's with the...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.83,0:20:18.25,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,"Like, you're finally showing up \Nin the twelfth episode?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.25,0:20:20.38,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I've been in it for, like, forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.38,0:20:21.46,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Ho. Ho. Ho."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.46,0:20:22.63,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...attitude you've got?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.63,0:20:24.21,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,A-Absolutely not!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.21,0:20:27.80,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,It's an honor to appear with \NAkira-sama in the actual show as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.97,0:20:29.93,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Appear?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.93,0:20:32.64,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,All you did this week was \Npick up a handkerchief, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.64,0:20:37.35,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't be thinking you've got\Nwhat it takes to make it in this business!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.35,0:20:40.15,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Don't forget that you can just disappear like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.81,0:20:42.52,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I-I'll keep that in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.36,0:20:44.78,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,After that announcement...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.78,0:20:46.19,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...you can't wait for the next episode!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.19,0:20:48.61,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,You want it now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.61,0:20:49.45,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Everyone is probably trembling...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.45,0:20:51.37,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Er, shaking naked in their boots in anticipation!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.37,0:20:52.03,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.03,0:20:54.04,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,We should treat our fans with care...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.04,0:20:57.04,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...and air it right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.04,0:20:59.54,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,We can grab a thirty minute slot, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.41,0:20:58.58,ls_alt,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.58,0:21:00.75,ls_alt,,0,0,0,,That'd be pushing it...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.54,0:21:01.29,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Pretty please?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.96,0:21:03.30,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Or forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.30,0:21:07.55,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,So send any messages to the \Nradio show or the home page!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.55,0:21:08.51,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Bye-bee!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.51,0:21:09.47,ls_alt,,0,0,0,,Bye-bee!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.14,0:21:12.01,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,What to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.01,0:21:14.14,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,It'd be bad if I overshadowed \Nthe main characters, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.14,0:21:15.43,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,It would indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.43,0:21:17.60,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,But there's a tendency for the \Nmain character's friends and rivals...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.60,0:21:21.81,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...to end up more popular than \Nthe actual main characters!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.06,0:21:23.52,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.52,0:21:24.40,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,A-Akira-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.40,0:21:25.36,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.36,0:21:25.98,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Aren't you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.98,0:21:26.49,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.49,0:21:27.24,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...talking about yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.03,0:21:31.53,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Don't get so full of yourself \N'cause you're popular lately!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.74,0:21:32.16,ls_alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8}No, absolutely not!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.53,0:21:33.74,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Don't expect this to last!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.16,0:21:33.99,ls_alt,,0,0,0,,No, never!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.74,0:21:36.16,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,You won't be placing first in the poll
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.20,0:21:36.83,ls_alt,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.16,0:21:38.29,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Don't mess with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.83,0:21:38.08,ls_alt,,0,0,0,,That's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.08,0:21:38.79,ls_alt,,0,0,0,,Listen to m—
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.96,0:21:49.93,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Next we have a duet from Tsukasa and Miyuki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.93,0:21:50.76,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Yuki-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.76,0:21:52.38,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Let's go up front to sing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.68,0:21:56.93,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,You chose a song for them to sing...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.93,0:21:58.02,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,How bizarre.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.02,0:22:00.64,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I know all kinds of songs.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.52,0:22:05.11,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,But it's still an anime song, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.11,0:22:08.57,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Anime songs actually come \Nin handy in these situations.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.39,0:22:43.65,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Not even close!
