Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.01,0:23:13.34,TS/EpTitle,,0,0,0,,{\pos(205.6,60.3)\fad(0,500)\blur0.7}Next Episode
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.88,0:23:13.34,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Well, next time on Lucky Star:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.90,0:23:14.34,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I'm Tsukasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.09,0:23:15.84,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.84,0:23:19.47,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I was really hungry one night...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.47,0:23:21.22,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...but it was really late...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.22,0:23:24.27,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...so I was wondering if I should eat something...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.27,0:23:27.81,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I finally decided a little bite would be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.81,0:23:29.57,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,And then I went to the kitchen...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.57,0:23:31.86,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...and I remembered I had some snacks left over...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.86,0:23:33.49,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...so I opened up the freezer...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.49,0:23:34.57,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I'm already out of time?!
